<br>
Murder is when he had to choose whether or not she would die at that moment, and chose to do it.  If it was entirely out of his control (car slides on icy road, kills pedestrian...) it is an accident.  That's in the eyes of US law, and most western nations as well (read up on the difference between murder and manslaughter).<br>
<br>
Further, what he did may be construed as premeditated murder (he was out to kill some people he didn't like that day, she just happened to be there?) as opposed to a &quot;murder of passion&quot; or whatnot.  That'd be a tougher argument to make.<br>
<br>
As far as &quot;personal&quot; attacks on this board, people are attacking your attitude and views, not you personally.  Fine line, I know, but its really more the sprit of the attack/debate... on the FB it's done to be either amusing or hurtful.  Here, it's done to make a point.  That's been my take on it, anyway.  Others' views will very likely differ.<br>
<br>
I hope you don't go running back to the FB - you actually do have a base of understanding of what you're talking about (not just ranting senselessly) and you bring an extreme viewpoint to this board which makes it all that much more interesting.  Just don't be so locked in your views that you are completely inflexible; only then does it become pointless to post on a board like this.  Otherwise, if everyone was a moderate here who generally agreed with one another, the board would die <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#4D4D4D><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub101.ezboard.com/bthetribunaldotorg.showUserPublicProfile?gid=wolvar>Wolvar</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_thatch.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>My third character is Lovawr</span><br>  Posts: 1798<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(3/19/03 10:52 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub101.ezboard.com/fthetribunaldotorgfrm36.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=498.topic&index=145>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Strange</span><hr size=1> Apparently Count16, you need to look up the definition of murder. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#333333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub101.ezboard.com/bthetribunaldotorg.showUserPublicProfile?gid=caledhontelrana>Caledhon TelRana</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>I read boards more<br>than I play EQ....</span><br>  Posts: 843<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(3/19/03 11:14 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub101.ezboard.com/ft